FY_Dedecagon

Spawns offer both teams identical paths to victory. This arena has three basic paths for the players to take, with various splits and possibilities at each. I've tried to pay attention to the possibilities of gameplay, offering fast rounds without any lame deaths.
  • Three main knife battle spots.
  • Two handgun locations for taking out the opposition's assault location.
  • Two assault rifle spots with a high vantagepoint, but with minimal (partially destroyable) cover.
  • Underwater route containing SMG's on either side.
Every route connects back to the others in a fun simplistic way to keep you battling for many rounds to come.
